cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with temporal logic specifications and their refinement.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of algorithms to automatically correct unrealizable specifications.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper deals with the synthesis of finite-state controllers for software systems.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of formal specifications and their refinement.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with the synthesis of controllers for systems.
